Ai Camera Tripod Guide


Contained in this guide is the following:

	Bill of Materials
	Printing Instructions

Bill of Meterials

	1x camera_mount.stl
	1x tilt_mount.stl
	1x tripod_swivel.stl
	1x tripod_base.stl
	2x lock_knob_0.25x20_bolts.stl (Optional is you want to use steel bolts)
		1X 1/4x20x3/4 Steel Hex Head Bolt
		1x 1/4x20x1-1/2 Steel Hex Head Bolt
	1x 025x20x08_swivel_lock_knob.stl (If you want to 3d print the bolt instead)
	1x 025x20x1.5_tilt_lock_knob.stl (If you want to 3d print the bolt instead)
	1x uno_holder.stl (Uno Skirt for additional arduino and breadboard mount)

Printing Instuctions

	All parts are designed to be printed without support.  You may have to reorient the the part to ensure proper results, below is a guide.
	
